trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of all [UsingTask](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) elements in a project.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en samling av alle [UsingTask](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) elementer i et prosjekt.

trans-unit.source: Copies the entire <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.UsingTaskCollection"></xref> to a compatible one-dimensional <xref:System.Array> of <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.UsingTask"></xref> objects, starting at the specified index of the target array.
trans-unit.target: Overfører hele <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.UsingTaskCollection"> </xref> til en kompatibel endimensjonal <xref:System.Array>av <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.UsingTask"> </xref> objekter, med Start fra den angitte indeksen på Målmatrisen.</xref:System.Array>

trans-unit.source: The one-dimensional <xref:System.Array> of <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.UsingTask"></xref> objects that is the destination of the elements copied from <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.UsingTaskCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Den endimensjonal <xref:System.Array>av <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.UsingTask"> </xref> objekter som er målet for elementene kopieres fra <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.UsingTaskCollection"> </xref>.</xref:System.Array>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Array> must have zero-based indexing.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Array>må ha nullbasert indeksering.</xref:System.Array>

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index in `array` at which copying begins.
trans-unit.target: Den nullbaserte indeksen i `array` som kopiering begynner.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index in `array` at which copying begins.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating the number of <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.UsingTask"></xref> objects in the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.UsingTaskCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir antall <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.UsingTask"> </xref> objekter i den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.UsingTaskCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Each <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.UsingTask> object in the collection represents a element in the project.
trans-unit.target: Hver <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.UsingTask>objektet i samlingen representerer et element i prosjektet.</xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.UsingTask>

trans-unit.source: An integer value representing the number of <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.UsingTask"></xref> objects in the collection.
trans-unit.target: En heltallsverdi som representerer antall <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.UsingTask"> </xref> objekter i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Gets an enumerator that iterates through the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.UsingTaskCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter en opplisting som går gjennom den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.UsingTaskCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This method allows the caller to use the `foreach` statement of the C# language (`for each` in [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)]) to iterate through the individual <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.UsingTask> objects in the <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.UsingTaskCollection>.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kan oppkalleren å bruke den `foreach` setningen med språket C# (`for each` i [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)]) å gå gjennom de individuelle <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.UsingTask>objekter i <xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.UsingTaskCollection>.</xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.UsingTaskCollection> </xref:Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.UsingTask>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator> for the entire <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.UsingTaskCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator>for hele <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.UsingTaskCollection"> </xref>.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator>

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether access to the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.UsingTaskCollection"></xref> is synchronized (thread safe).
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om tilgang til den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.UsingTaskCollection"> </xref> er synkronisert (tråden trygt).

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if access to the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.BuildEngine.UsingTaskCollection"></xref> is synchronized (thread safe); otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.

trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
